data.description: Welcome to this charming 3-bedroom home situated in the serene Carolina Trace gated community in Sanford. Upon entering, you'll be greeted by an inviting open floor plan that effortlessly combines the living, dining and kitchen areas. The heart of the home is the expansive family room with cathedral ceilings and fireplace — the perfect setting for family gatherings or quiet evenings in.  With its 3 bedrooms, including a primary suite with en-suite bathroom, this home offers an idyllic modern living space. Step outside through the sliding glass doors to the extensive deck and sizable backyard. Whether you’re entertaining or seeking a peaceful retreat, the yard is a beautiful backdrop for outdoor serenity.  Close proximity to full-service country club, golf course, walking trails, lake and swimming pool.
